To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private IntradayVwap _vwap;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_vwap = VWAP(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_vwap.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "VWAP Current", _vwap.Current);
}
